channel.title: Completely unsure whats wrong with it
channel.description: Im unsure whats wrong with my server, It worked for like a week or so. Now it won't connect even the slightest. My Run Command Prompt doesn't say anything about anyone even trying to connect it just stays blank. It worked one day, My power went out for a while. And now no one can log on.

item.title: Completely unsure whats wrong with it
item.dc:creator: @SheppehSays SheppehSays
item.description:
@SheppehSays wrote:

[quote=“x blitz x, post:2, topic:257069”]Dynamic IP address might have changed. You remember port forwarding, you had to enter a number like ‘192.168.1.2’.
Check that.[/quote]
Oh thanks. It did. fixed now.

Read full topic
